item.title: Privacy Policy
item.author: nova@scene.to (Nova Annabella)
item.description: Privacy Policy Introduction This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, process, and share your information when you use our webpage hosted on GitHub Pages. It also explains your rights with respect to your information and how to exercise those rights. Information Collection and Use We do not collect or store any personal information from our users. The webpage is designed to generate random images and does not require any personal information to be entered by the user.
